 *        _____________________________
 *       |  ARDUINO UNO >>>   SIM800L  |
 *        -----------------------------
 *            GND      >>>   GND
 *        RX  10       >>>   TX    
 *        TX  11       >>>   RX
 *       RESET 2       >>>   RST 
 *                 
 *   POWER SOURCE 4.2V >>> VCC
